  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested product research for WOCA wood care products (Intensive Wood Cleaner and Natural Soap) with shipping to Switzerland. Manus conducted comprehensive price comparison across Swiss retailers, created shopping carts to calculate exact shipping costs, and identified Holzpunkt-Parkett.ch as the optimal vendor with CHF 67.70 total for both products including delivery.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser needed to source WOCA wood care products for delivery to Switzerland, seeking best prices and shipping rates\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nComprehensive product research across Swiss retailers, price comparison analysis, shopping cart creation for shipping calculation, optimization recommendations for bulk purchasing to achieve free shipping threshold\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [analysis] Price Comparison Report — Detailed comparison of WOCA products across Swiss retailers with shipping costs\n- [recommendation] Purchasing Strategy — Optimal vendor selection and bulk purchase recommendations for cost savings\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Selected Holzpunkt-Parkett.ch as primary vendor\n- Recommended 2.5L formats for free shipping threshold\n- Prioritized next-day delivery capability\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Real shopping cart creation for accurate shipping calculation\n- Identification of volume discounts and free shipping thresholds\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Holzpunkt-Parkett.ch offers 10% automatic online discount\n- Free shipping threshold at CHF 100 creates significant savings opportunity\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Final quantity decision for optimal bulk purchasing\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Place order with selected vendor\n- Consider bulk purchase for free shipping savings\n---\nUID: a2MPXJiDZSV12FnGpZFtiD | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0132\n"
}